inoremap jk <esc>
" may interfering with scrolling in message:
mnoremap jk <esc>
vnoremap jk <esc>
cnoremap jk <esc>

noremap <C-h> gT
noremap <C-l> gt

" space as empty keypress to finish waiting if jk was intended:
mnoremap J 12j<space>
mnoremap K 12k
mnoremap H 12h
mnoremap L 12l

mnoremap r <esc>lrm

